data.description: This charming Swiss Chalet home has a warm and inviting feel with wood floors throughout. The main level of the home features a large living room with wood-burning inset stove providing ample heat and cozy ambiance, 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom. The upper level features the kitchen with hand-crafted concrete counter tops, dining room with a wood-burning fire place and flex space. 1 bedroom and 1 full bathroom in addition to a bright and large master suite featuring a spa themed bathroom, huge walk-in closet and office nook. Soak in the sunlight from the first and second floor sliders connecting you to nature-themed outdoor spaces for entertaining. Oversized garage allows for vehicle, storage, a large home gym. Enjoy privacy in the wooded back yard featuring a 220v powered workshop, massive 2 story storage shed, and large wooded camp site. Seller is offering a $6,000 contractor credit at settlement to upgrade anything you choose. Deck is wired for a hot tub.
